[{"id":1,"user_id":54,"text":"<p>Will .dbf be covnverted to SPSS?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":30,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2015-10-28 15:12:56 UTC","updated_at":"2015-10-28 15:12:56 UTC"},{"id":4,"user_id":1623,"text":"<p>test annotation</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":556,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-09-08 20:29:54 UTC","updated_at":"2016-09-08 20:29:54 UTC"},{"id":5,"user_id":3060,"text":"<p>share ideas and&nbsp;feedback when co-writing plans...</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":1112,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-05-04 05:41:17 UTC","updated_at":"2016-05-04 05:41:17 UTC"},{"id":14,"user_id":2806,"text":"<p>test&nbsp;</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":1291,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-09-12 19:06:22 UTC","updated_at":"2016-09-12 19:06:22 UTC"},{"id":15,"user_id":159,"text":"<p>Test d'annotation</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":1293,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-05-30 15:28:09 UTC","updated_at":"2017-05-30 15:28:09 UTC"},{"id":20,"user_id":3439,"text":"<p>ceci est un nouveau commentaires</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":1359,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2015-11-06 19:49:36 UTC","updated_at":"2015-11-06 19:49:36 UTC"},{"id":83,"user_id":3767,"text":"<p>I would suggest using the data audit table that you prepared in Ottawa here. That way you've connected each form of data to its file type. This in turn might help with deciding which forms&nbsp;of data are easiest to share technically.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":2174,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-04-28 09:47:32 UTC","updated_at":"2016-04-28 09:47:32 UTC"},{"id":142,"user_id":3468,"text":"<p>This is an area that we should discuss. I haven't been following anything, but could go back and revise and clean up.&nbsp;</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":2864,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-09-30 17:04:40 UTC","updated_at":"2016-09-30 17:04:40 UTC"},{"id":144,"user_id":3468,"text":"<p>This feels like a repeat of some of the earlier questions - what if the point.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":2871,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-09-30 18:39:08 UTC","updated_at":"2016-09-30 18:39:08 UTC"},{"id":146,"user_id":3942,"text":"<p>How much memory do we need?&nbsp; seems like audio = 800GB, doubled for the editing, to 1600</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":2985,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-10-26 20:29:00 UTC","updated_at":"2016-10-26 20:29:00 UTC"},{"id":147,"user_id":3942,"text":"<p>We need to implement this organization system, pronto.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":2986,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-10-26 20:33:39 UTC","updated_at":"2016-10-26 20:33:39 UTC"},{"id":206,"user_id":4324,"text":"<p>test</p>","archived":1,"answer_id":3656,"archived_by":4324,"created_at":"2016-11-24 23:49:31 UTC","updated_at":"2016-11-24 23:50:15 UTC"},{"id":226,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Marie : Il serait utile d'avoir un dictionnaire ou lexique ou un guide pour savoir quelles sont les d&eacute;finitions des diff&eacute;rentes types de donn&eacute;es, notamment celles donn&eacute;es en exemple.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3856,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 17:18:58 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 17:18:58 UTC"},{"id":227,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Marie : C&ocirc;t&eacute; ergonomique, il serait bien d'avoir une plus grande fen&ecirc;tre de r&eacute;ponse pour faciliter le travail. L'utilisateur devrait pouvoir voir toute sa r&eacute;ponse.<br /><br />Aussi, il faudrait que l'enregistrement soit automatique (comme Google doc, par exemple), ou du moins qu'on puisse sauvegarder une annotation ind&eacute;pendamment d'une r&eacute;ponse. Je viens de perdre ma r&eacute;ponse en enregistrant mon annotation.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3856,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 17:27:24 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 17:27:24 UTC"},{"id":228,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Encore une fois, un petit guide produit par l'UQAM serait utile. Par exemple, les bases de donn&eacute;es peuvent &ecirc;tre sauvegard&eacute;es dans tel tel et tel format, mais tel format est pr&eacute;f&eacute;rable pour telle raison. Les fichiers vid&eacute;os peuvent &ecirc;tre sauvegard&eacute; dans tel tel tel format, mais tel format est pr&eacute;f&eacute;rable pour X raison.<br /><br />Les liens fournis sont quand m&ecirc;me bien utiles &agrave; ce sujet, l'UQAM pourrait s'en inspirer.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3857,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 17:33:28 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 19:50:05 UTC"},{"id":229,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Encore une fois, le document fourni par UBC est utile, surtout pour justifier les pratiques. L'UQAM devrait s'en inspirer pour produire un tel guide.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3858,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 17:51:26 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 19:51:03 UTC"},{"id":230,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Difficile de savoir quel niveau de pr&eacute;cision est requis ou demand&eacute; ici. l'UQAM pourrait produire un guide des bonnes pratiques, offrir des exemples, ou des \"templates\".</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3859,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 18:05:53 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 19:54:04 UTC"},{"id":231,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Un exemple plus concret serait utile pour cette question. L'UQAM pourrait fournir cela.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3860,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 18:12:09 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 19:55:06 UTC"},{"id":232,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Un exemple serait fort utile. Comment une autre &eacute;quipe comme la n&ocirc;tre a-t-elle fait?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3864,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 18:30:35 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 18:30:35 UTC"},{"id":233,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Encore une fois, un exemple de r&eacute;ponse serait grandement utile. L'UQAM pourrait pr&eacute;parer cela, ou du moins d&eacute;construire en &eacute;tapes recommand&eacute;es/ communes le processus.</p>\r\n<p>Les informations sur l'anonymisation fournies par le UK Data Archive sont tr&egrave;s int&eacute;ressantes. Elles devraient &ecirc;tre fournies aux auxiliaire de recherche - id&eacute;alement l'UQAM les auraient traduites :)</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3866,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 21:23:53 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 21:30:22 UTC"},{"id":234,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Une seconde r&eacute;vision des verbatims risque d'&ecirc;tre tr&egrave;s co&ucirc;teuse. Comment l'&eacute;viter, sans perdre des informations pertinentes pour l'analyse?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3866,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 21:27:24 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 21:27:24 UTC"},{"id":235,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>&nbsp;Les directives pour cette question incluent des liens qui m&egrave;nent &agrave; une tr&egrave;s grande quantit&eacute; d'information. Ce qui est super, si on a le temps de tout lire.<br />L'UQAM pourrait identifier les licences communes pour chaque discipline, de plus que d'indiquer les coordonn&eacute;es de la personne ressource &agrave; ce sujet.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3868,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 21:44:53 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 21:44:53 UTC"},{"id":236,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>&nbsp;Ce que je comprends, c'est que les licences peuvent permettre diff&eacute;rents niveaux d'accessibilit&eacute;. Voir :</p>\r\n<p>https://creativecommons.org/choose/</p>\r\n<p>Donc quel niveau est requis par le CRSH? Acces complet?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3868,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 21:46:58 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 21:46:58 UTC"},{"id":237,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>L'UQAM pourrait fournir des exemples plus concretes. <br />Je n'ai pas lu les liens dans les directives (manque de temps).</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3869,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 21:47:52 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 21:51:08 UTC"},{"id":238,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>L'UQAM devrait fournir une liste des formations offertes qui pourraient &ecirc;tre utiles aux gens responsables, ainsi que des livres ou autres formes d'instructions disponibles &agrave; la biblioth&egrave;que (p.ex. vid&eacute;os).<br />Les coordonn&eacute;es de la personne responsable devrait aussi &ecirc;tre inscrite ici.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3870,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 22:00:56 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 22:00:56 UTC"},{"id":239,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Que signifie : \"le d&eacute;partement ou la division qui supervise cette recherche en assumera la responsabilit&eacute;\" (voir directives)? Dans le cas du changement du directeur de projet, ou dans d'autres cas?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3871,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 22:06:01 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 22:06:01 UTC"},{"id":240,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>L'UQAM pourrait fournir un exemple concret de \"processus &agrave; suivre\" dans le cas du changement de direction ou de personnel important &agrave; la gestion des donn&eacute;es.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3871,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 22:08:42 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 22:08:42 UTC"},{"id":241,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>Il faut voir si CRSH explicite le soutient qu'ils vont fournir &agrave; la PGD (voir directives).</p>\r\n<p>L'UQAM pourrait fournir une liste des d&eacute;penses &agrave; pr&eacute;voir plus d&eacute;taill&eacute;e (p.ex. qu'est-ce que les prestations d'acc&egrave;s) et aussi une id&eacute;e des prix pour chaque &eacute;l&eacute;ment, afin de justement faciliter la pr&eacute;paration d'un budget r&eacute;aliste.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3872,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 22:16:42 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 22:16:42 UTC"},{"id":242,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>L'UQAM pourrait fournir des informations similaires &agrave; celles fournies par le UK Data Archive dans cette section.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3874,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 23:19:21 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 23:19:21 UTC"},{"id":243,"user_id":4383,"text":"<p>L'UQAM devrait fournir les coordonn&eacute;es des personnes et services &agrave; l'UQAM qui peuvent aider &agrave; r&eacute;pondre aux questions.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":3875,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2016-12-18 23:17:28 UTC","updated_at":"2016-12-18 23:17:28 UTC"},{"id":280,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Sugg&eacute;rer des ressources en fran&ccedil;ais lorsqu'elles existent. Par exemple : BNF. Format de donn&eacute;es pour la pr&eacute;servation num&eacute;rique. <a href=\"http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html</a></p>","archived":1,"answer_id":4330,"archived_by":2996,"created_at":"2017-01-23 14:32:03 UTC","updated_at":"2017-01-27 18:53:36 UTC"},{"id":281,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Des directives UQAM proposeraient des ressources en fran&ccedil;ais lorsqu'elles existent. Par exemple : BNF. Format de donn&eacute;es pour la pr&eacute;servation num&eacute;rique. <a href=\"http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html</a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4330,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-01-27 18:54:29 UTC","updated_at":"2017-01-27 18:54:29 UTC"},{"id":292,"user_id":194,"text":"<p>Suivant la version 13 de la norme du Conseil canadien de pataphysique. Gaston, peux-tu v&eacute;rifier?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4364,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-01-26 01:52:48 UTC","updated_at":"2017-01-26 01:52:48 UTC"},{"id":317,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Une personne-ressource du Service des biblioth&egrave;ques peut vous aider &agrave; trouver les informations n&eacute;cessaires &agrave; la compl&eacute;tion de ce plan.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Eveline Pilon (pilon.eveline@uqam.ca)</li>\r\n</ul>","archived":1,"answer_id":4409,"archived_by":4603,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:15:43 UTC","updated_at":"2017-03-31 18:12:09 UTC"},{"id":319,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Autres ressources&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Cornell University. Recommended File Formats for eCommons. <a href=\"https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format\" target=\"_blank\">https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format</a></p>\r\n<p>BNF. Format de donn&eacute;es pour la pr&eacute;servation num&eacute;rique. <a href=\"http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html</a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4410,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:24:54 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 15:24:54 UTC"},{"id":320,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Le Service des archives et de gestion des documents de l&rsquo;UQAM offre une formation intitul&eacute;e &laquo;&nbsp;Bonne pratiques de gestion des documents num&eacute;riques&nbsp;&raquo; qui couvre le contenu de cette question.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4411,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:30:21 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 15:30:21 UTC"},{"id":321,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Rappel : Une personne-ressource du Service des biblioth&egrave;ques peut vous aider &agrave; trouver les informations n&eacute;cessaires &agrave; la compl&eacute;tion de ce plan.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Eveline Pilon (pilon.eveline@uqam.ca)</li>\r\n</ul>","archived":0,"answer_id":4412,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:33:10 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 15:33:10 UTC"},{"id":322,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Les Services informatiques ont une offre de services en soutien &agrave; la recherche. Ils pourront vous aider &agrave; d&eacute;terminer vos besoins de stockage et &agrave; mettre en place l&rsquo;infrastructure n&eacute;cessaire &agrave; votre projet de recherche.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche\" target=\"_blank\">https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche</a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4415,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:50:54 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 15:53:31 UTC"},{"id":323,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Les Services informatiques&nbsp;pourront vous assister dans l'&eacute;laboration de votre strat&eacute;gie de sauvegarde.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\">https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche</span></a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4416,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 16:51:06 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 16:51:06 UTC"},{"id":324,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Les Services informatiques&nbsp;pourront vous aider &agrave; mettre au point les strat&eacute;gies de collaboration et de s&eacute;curit&eacute; entre vos diff&eacute;rents espaces de travail.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\">https://servicesinformatiques.uqam.ca/services/Exploitation%20pour%20la%20Recherche</span></a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4417,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 18:28:07 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 18:28:07 UTC"},{"id":325,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Une personne-ressource du Service des biblioth&egrave;ques peut vous aider &agrave; identifier les d&eacute;p&ocirc;ts pertinents pour vos donn&eacute;es.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Eveline Pilon (pilon.eveline@uqam.ca)</li>\r\n</ul>","archived":0,"answer_id":4418,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 19:02:29 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 19:02:29 UTC"},{"id":326,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Autres ressources&nbsp;(signal&eacute;es d&eacute;j&agrave; en 1.2):</p>\r\n<p>Cornell University. Recommended File Formats for eCommons. <a href=\"https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\">https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format</span></a></p>\r\n<p>BNF. Format de donn&eacute;es pour la pr&eacute;servation num&eacute;rique. <a href=\"http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\">http://www.bnf.fr/fr/professionnels/preservation_numerique_boite_outils/a.pres_num_formats.html</span></a></p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4419,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 19:05:52 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 19:05:52 UTC"},{"id":327,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Pensons-nous avoir&nbsp;des exigences institutionnelles...</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4420,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 19:08:56 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 19:08:56 UTC"},{"id":328,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Ressources UQAM: Comit&eacute;s d'&eacute;thique / Service des affaires juridiques /&nbsp;&nbsp; Service des partenariats et du soutien &agrave; l&rsquo;innovation (SePSI) pour les questions de propri&eacute;t&eacute; intellectuelle dans le cadre d'un partenariat.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":4427,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 19:18:16 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 19:18:16 UTC"},{"id":329,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Une personne-ressource du Service des biblioth&egrave;ques peut vous aider &agrave; trouver les informations n&eacute;cessaires &agrave; la compl&eacute;tion de ce plan.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Eveline Pilon (pilon.eveline@uqam.ca)</li>\r\n</ul>","archived":0,"answer_id":4428,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2017-02-03 15:15:46 UTC","updated_at":"2017-02-03 15:19:12 UTC"},{"id":330,"user_id":2996,"text":"<p>Autres ressources&nbsp;:</p>\r\n<p>Cornell University. Recommended File Formats for eCommons. <a href=\"https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format\" target=\"_blank\">https://ecommons.cornell.edu/page/support#format</a></p>\r\n<p>BNF. Format de donn&eacute;es pour la pr&eacute;servation n