p>Are we? Should we be?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39876,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:30:04 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:30:04 UTC"},{"id":3784,"user_id":22316,"text":"<p>I have no idea how to estimate the amount of space we will need. The current version of the Environmental Scan document is 55.3KB and it is not yet complete.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39877,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:32:49 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:32:49 UTC"},{"id":3785,"user_id":22316,"text":"<p>I do not know if this is up to me?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39883,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:36:39 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:36:39 UTC"},{"id":3786,"user_id":22316,"text":"<p>Thoughts? Recommendations?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39884,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:37:21 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:37:21 UTC"},{"id":3787,"user_id":22316,"text":"<p>Thoughts? Recommendations?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39886,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:37:53 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:37:53 UTC"},{"id":3788,"user_id":22316,"text":"<p>Since we're using OneDrive, there should be very few to no associated costs, correct?</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":39887,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-22 19:38:48 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-22 19:38:48 UTC"},{"id":3789,"user_id":22383,"text":"<p>Unsure of the timeline and amount of storage needed</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":40053,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-24 16:24:27 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-24 16:24:27 UTC"},{"id":3790,"user_id":22305,"text":"<p>This is outside my knowledge and abilities to begin.</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":40093,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-24 18:18:06 UTC","updated_at":"2022-05-24 18:18:06 UTC"},{"id":3791,"user_id":22305,"text":"<p>It is likely unhelpful for me to decide/dictate this for the research team.&nbsp;</p>","archived":0,"answer_id":40094,"archived_by":null,"created_at":"2022-05-24 